Sabre growled and attacked transforming he rapped himself around her 
hoping to bring them both down...

NightViper laughed as the blasts tore away at his reptile skin 
showing the metal mechanics beneath. "Pain isss only in the head 
bidie." He lunged forward sinking his fangs into Windlord.

Rave transformed and like wise grappled starstorm as WingRazor 
managed to land hard, but not fataly.
